'''Antiox breath masks''',<ref name="2015Topps">{{Topps|set=2015 Topps Star Wars Chrome Perspectives|cardname=Plo Koon|link=https://www.tcdb.com/ViewCard.cfm/sid/114595/cid/8022612/2015-Topps-Chrome-Star-Wars-Perspectives-Jedi-vs.-Sith-8-J-Plo-Koon}}</ref> or '''Antiox masks''', were specialized [[breath mask]]s worn by members of the [[Kel Dor]] [[species]] to survive in [[oxygen]]-rich [[atmosphere]]s.<ref name="Character Encyclopedia">''[[Star Wars Character Encyclopedia: Updated and Expanded]]''</ref> They were a special variant of the [[A99 aquata breather]].<ref name="Lightsabers and Jedi Equipment">{{EncyclopediaCite|Lightsabers and Jedi Equipment}}</ref> The patterns on these masks were unique to Kel Dor clans.<ref name="Complete Visual Dictionary, New Edition">''[[Star Wars: The Complete Visual Dictionary, New Edition]]''</ref>

[[Plo Koon]]<ref name="Visual Encyclopedia">''[[Star Wars: The Visual Encyclopedia]]''</ref> and [[Bo Keevil]]<ref name="The Recruit">{{Resistance|The Recruit}}</ref> wore metal masks and goggles as a life-support device<ref name="Visual Encyclopedia" /> to protect their sensitive eyes, lungs,<ref name="Ultimate Star Wars">''[[Ultimate Star Wars]]''</ref> and nostrils from the oxygen-rich atmosphere of [[Coruscant]] and other [[planet]]s when away from their [[homeworld]] of [[Dorin]].<ref name="Character Encyclopedia" />

